# Quality Iteration Workflow

The authoritative process is `iterations/WORKFLOW.md`. The only comparable
baseline is `iterations/current-baseline.json`, explained in
`iterations/CURRENT_BASELINE.md`.

At session start, read those files and the active iteration directory only. Do
not bulk-read `DECISION_HISTORY.md` or Git history unless the proposed idea or a
user question requires historical context.

The next iteration is `iter-021`. A score may be compared with the baseline only
when its evaluation protocol ID matches exactly; otherwise rebaseline first.
